COMMENT ON TABLE OFFENDER_CHARGES IS 'Identifies all charges within an offender''s legal case. While there may be many events associated with a charge, and many records on court_event_charges to record court events and historical dispositions on that charge, this record identifies the charge uniquely, and summarizes the current status of the charge.';
